'''H'Kak bean tea''' was a fragrant orange-colored [[Tea/Legends|tea]] derived from [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]] [[H'Kak bean]]s. It was ingested for its relaxing and detoxifying effects. The beverage was known to be served at the [[Cleft Head]] wake-up house during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]].

